# Move robot to target pose — long-running action with progress feedback

# Goal
float32 target_x
float32 target_y
float32 target_theta
float32 max_speed
---
# Result
bool    reached
float32 final_x
float32 final_y
float32 elapsed_time
---
# Feedback
float32 current_x
float32 current_y
float32 distance_remaining
float32 percent_complete
